Name: Drain Bladder
Description:
Small bladder for unclogging drains.

Instructions:

  • Make sure sealing washer in the bladder joint in place.
  • Attach drain cleaning bladder to a garden hose connected to a cold water faucet.
  • Place into blocked drain pipe aluminimum of 6 inches.
  • Turn on the cold water slowly to full pressure. Hold until the clog is cleared.
  • Turn off the water and wait until the drain cleaning bladder is fully deflated before removing. If water backs up, shut water off immediately.
